sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as User/Controller
    participant PRC as Pricing
    participant PROC as Process Managers
    participant INV as Inventory
    participant FULF as Fulfillment
    participant PAY as Payments
    participant SHIP as Shipping
    participant INVC as Invoicing
    participant STOR as Stores

    Note over UI,STOR: 1. Draft & Build Order
    UI->>PRC: DraftOffer
    PRC-->>PRC: OfferDrafted
    UI->>PRC: AddPriceItem (per product)
    PRC-->>PRC: PriceItemAdded
    PRC-->>PROC: TotalOrderValue calculates total
    PROC-->>PROC: TotalOrderValueUpdated
    PROC-->>PAY: SetPaymentAmount

    Note over UI,STOR: 2. Promotions (automatic)
    PRC-->>PROC: PriceItemAdded triggers
    PROC->>PRC: SetTimePromotionDiscount (ApplyTimePromotion)
    PROC->>PRC: MakeProductFreeForOrder (ThreePlusOneFree)

    Note over UI,STOR: 3. Accept Offer & Reserve Stock
    UI->>PRC: AcceptOffer
    PRC-->>PRC: OfferAccepted
    PRC-->>PROC: ReservationProcess triggered
    PROC->>INV: Reserve (per product)
    PROC->>FULF: RegisterOrder

    Note over UI,STOR: 4. Payment
    UI->>PAY: AuthorizePayment
    PAY-->>PAY: PaymentAuthorized
    UI->>PAY: CapturePayment
    PAY-->>PAY: PaymentCaptured
    PAY-->>PROC: ConfirmOrderOnPaymentCaptured
    PROC->>FULF: ConfirmOrder

    Note over UI,STOR: 5. Fulfill & Ship
    FULF-->>FULF: OrderConfirmed
    FULF-->>PROC: ReservationProcess dispatches
    PROC->>INV: Dispatch (per product)
    FULF-->>PROC: ShipmentProcess triggered
    PROC->>SHIP: SubmitShipment
    PROC->>SHIP: AuthorizeShipment

    Note over UI,STOR: 6. Invoice
    FULF-->>PROC: InvoiceGeneration triggered
    PROC->>STOR: RegisterInvoice
    PROC->>INVC: AddInvoiceItem (per product)
